{
  "stem": "1975.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 77.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because many POWs-- POWs were betrayed in many cases.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So me, he gave like royal treatment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Beside that-- next to the-- When the front got a little closer, there were two Jewish-- there was a Jewish captain an a Jewish lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they, right away, when we identified our self, they told me right away that I should not stay here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I should go more to the east because they say the front is very, very uncertain.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It might shift from one place to the other one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he says you have suffered plenty in your life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There's no reason that after you are now safe, you should not be-- I mean, you should not give up your life.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Of course, later on, I found out it was in the Russian army, there were many anti-Semites also.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But this group, especially those people who are the front runners, who are in the sense-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] they have the reconnaissance, they are much more human than some other troops where I served later.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They truthfully were really concerned with us, and they gave us a Studebaker, which they had later on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Everything, the Jeeps and Studebakers, and the food was made in the USA.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Most of those-- many people don't know that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "That was worked out, was between Roosevelt and Stalin that the land lease.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And you already heard about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russian, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then they send us a little bit farther down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the matter of a week, they stormed in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came into Kovno and they took over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They liberated Kovno.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my first intention was I run to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I run to the place where I used to live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The ghetto was destroyed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Most of the houses were exploded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the bunkers were exploded.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
